      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SEARING LIGHT ran third last start at Ascot Park Raceway over 2200m, beaten 50 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Facing a tougher assignment but she is capable of running a big race. 3. PACIFIC ARC was in the money at this track two runs ago before having his colours lowered at his latest appearance over 2200m at Ascot Park Raceway, beaten 55 metres. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Won't find this any harder and he can bounce back straight away. 6. RAMBLIN ROVER is on the radar after his last-start fifth over 1980m at Addington eight days ago. 2. BOMBAY GLACIER could only finish sixth over 2400m at this track most recently. Open to improvement and is in the mix.\",\"runners\":[1,3,6,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
